{"tid":176223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[28/3]黃大仙女企跳；駿景園男高處墮下身亡；元朗男吊頸昏迷","createTime":"2017-03-28T05:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T08:59:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36f0d2255a6d2e6784e8a07a2524574ea6be8625","tid":176223,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"黃大仙女子 激動危坐窗邊<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙橫頭磡邨宏安樓，凌晨5時許，一名姓陳25歲女子，攀出窗口危坐，情緒激動企圖自殺，街坊見狀報警，警員接報趕至現場游說，女子被消防拉回安全地方，由救護員送院治理。警方正調查其企圖自殺原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56489340&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56489340%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f05afd1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56489340%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&h=00090fa0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56489340&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328</a><br />\n<br />\n男子駿景園墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n火炭駿景園1座，今早10時35分，一名中年男子被發現由大廈高處墮下，重傷倒卧平台，救護員接報到場證實男子當場死亡，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56490061&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56490061%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d62f2edc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56490061%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&h=f7e45ca4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56490061&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗男子吊頸 昏迷送院<br />\n<br />\n元朗盛屋村萬華花園，上午11時半，一名男子在單位內吊頸自殺。救護員到場將他送院搶救，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56490188&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56490188%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=26fe7f46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56490188%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170328&h=2cb471bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56490188&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170328</a>"},{"pid":"a789c0afed017dac3d496e30dc5cd19fa1dcc707","tid":176223,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b694f75c31370be039d2be96b59fdb059976c5a","tid":176223,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"已經唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90f326d3202823cc00cd7da21fd259bce450841","tid":176223,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f5de5fa52d8e80b58ac5dde55b2faaa6c575da9","tid":176223,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0